BANKS, George (61, marble polisher), and 





BANKS, Alice Maud (34, machinist); 

George Banks being a male person unlawfully carnally knowing 



   Alice Maud Banks, who was to his knowledge his daughter; 

Alice Maud Banks being a female person, unlawfully permitting 


   George Banks to have carnal knowledge of her, she then well knowing him to be her father.
